snippet.title: RPG Maker 2000- Another Moon Whistle (1/2)
snippet.description: This is a digest movie of "Another Moon Whistle" which is made by RPG Tkool 2000(=Japanese version of RPG Maker 2k). All texts are Japanese, but you may feel Japanese nostalgic atmosphere.アナザームーンホイッスルから溢れるノスタルジーを味わってください。
